Distribution Package Scripts
----------------------------

This folder provides scripts and specification files used to create packages to
easily distribute Django-Flash in several Distributions or Operating Systems.


ABS (Arch Build System)
-----------------------

    http://wiki.archlinux.org/index.php/The_Arch_package_making_HOW-TO_-_with_guidelines
    http://wiki.archlinux.org/index.php/Python_Package_Guidelines


DEB (Debian package)
--------------------

    https://wiki.ubuntu.com/PackagingGuide/Python
    http://wiki.debian.org/DebianPython/NewPolicy


RPM (RPM Package Manager)
-------------------------

    http://fedoraproject.org/wiki/How_to_create_an_RPM_package
